oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Civil War dug relics from various locations around Bledsoe County, Tennessee
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This collection includes: one US coat button, one US cuff button, one round ball, one US three ring mnie ball, one complete Spencer cartridge, one fired Enfield bullet, one fired three ring minie, one iron roller buckle, one minie ball and a part of a US spur all dug from Bledsoe County, Tennessee.
